		e('+-')0s(N)1s(N)9s('*')6s(F)3e2s('+')7s(N)5s(N)8s('*')6s3e4 = <PROUT '4'><Cast<AddNew(e0s1s9)s5s8>s6s3e2e4>
		e('+-')0s(N)1s(N)9s('-+')5e2s('-')4s(N)6s(N)8s('-+')7e3 = <PROUT '5'><Cast<SubNew(e0s1s9)s6s8>s5e2s7e3>
